nodes.text: A male Muun was captured after the Battle of Muunilinst. He provided a code to the Galactic Republic in order to see holographic transmissions sent to Trade Federation Viceroy Nute Gunray's Neimoidian mechno-chair's holotransceiver.

Leland Chee has said it was the intent for the Muun mentioned in Labyrinth of Evil to be one of the Muuns seen in Star Wars: Clone Wars, but without a name in either source, it's unknown which Muun it is.
